value: The project ID of the project that contains the table
The name of the dataset that contains the table, also referred to as the datasetId
The name of the table, also referred to as the tableId
A single partition's ID. For unpartitioned tables, the value is NULL. For partitioned tables that contain rows with NULL values in the partitioning column, the value is __NULL__.
The total number of rows in the partition
The total number of logical bytes in the partition
The total number of billable bytes in the partition
The time when the data was most recently written to the partition
The partition's storage tier - ACTIVE: the partition is billed as active storage; LONG_TERM: the partition is billed as long-term storage
